description:
Miotabot x Cardanobot

"miotabot" a change from bees, robots can be used to detect land mines. Because, this robot can smell trinitrotoluene or TNT from a distance of 100 kilometers. These two facts show that this robot is very careful and very sensitive to potential dangers. The bee collects enemy armor And amazingly, wherever he lands, not a single enemy is damaged. Instead of destroying, this robot actually helps other robots heal.

"Cardanobot" has 6 Chimneys, which allows him to fly at the speed of an F-16 aircraft, with rigid springs. cardanobot can jump at the speed of ultrasonic reflection. whoever is near it will surely be destroyed
